* does
	* reads in Nigeria, WAVE 3 (2015-2016) POST PLANTING, NIGERIA AG SECT11C1
	* determines planting (not harvest) labor for rainy season
	* outputs clean data file ready for combination with wave 3 plot data

* assumes
	* customsave.ado
	* mdesc.ado
	
